# CommonJS for JavaScript Files

JavaScript files (.js) use CommonJS: `require()` and `module.exports`.
TypeScript files (.ts/.tsx) use ES modules: `import/export`.
Path alias: `stremio/*` maps to `src/*`.
4-space indentation, single quotes, semicolons required.
